  "body": "https://www.figma.com/file/idUoxN7OIW2Jpp3PMJ1Rl8/%E2%9A%99%EF%B8%8F-Settings-%7C-Desktop?node-id=15235%3A285624&mode=dev\r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/idUoxN7OIW2Jpp3PMJ1Rl8/%E2%9A%99%EF%B8%8F-Settings-%7C-Desktop?node-id=15285%3A324706&mode=dev\r\n\r\nCovers migrating profile or seed phrase related keypair to a Keycard from the Settings/Wallet, as well as migrating them from a keycard to the app.\r\n\r\nCorresponding options for those keyapairs:\r\n- `Move keypair to Keycard`\r\n- `Stop using Keycard`",
